    <title type="html"><![CDATA[Setting the hostname in Arch Linux]]></title>
    <link href="http://pfigue.github.io/blog/2012/12/27/setting-the-hostname-in-arch-linux/"/>
    <updated>2012-12-27T12:55:00+01:00</updated>
    <id>http://pfigue.github.io/blog/2012/12/27/setting-the-hostname-in-arch-linux</id>
    <content type="html"><![CDATA[<p>Set a hostname:</p>

<pre><code>$ sudo hostnamectl set-hostname my-pretty-cow
</code></pre>

<p>Get the hostname (Linux standard):</p>

<pre><code>$ hostname [-f]
</code></pre>

<p>See <a href="https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/Network_Configuration#Set_the_hostname">Network Configuration: Set the hostname</a></p>
